<item>
            <title>[DERBY-5542] Remove checks for Java version being greater than or equal to 1.4</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5542</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The code contains some checks for JVMInfo.JDK_ID &amp;gt;= JVMInfo.J2SE_14. That condition evaluates to true on all currently supported platforms (including on CDC/FP), so the checks can be removed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12535296">DERBY-5542</key>
            <summary>Remove checks for Java version being greater than or equal to 1.4</summary>
